references: Repealing: Ord 90952, Ord 94622, Ord 98639, Ord 99195, Ord 100057, Ord 103513, Ord 103881
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the licensing and regulating of ambulance services, repealing Sections 010, 020, 030, 040, 050, 060, 070, 080, 090, 100, 110, 120, 130, 140, 150 and 160 of Chapter 6.76 of the Seattle Municipal Code and Ordinances 90952, 94622, 98639, 99195, 100057, 103513 and 103881, and any other ordinances or parts thereof in conflict herewith.
